{"content":[{"id":"5d3d0a71","settings":{"display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"c9a15d8"}]},"elements":[{"id":"5f8950dd","settings":{"editor":"<p>Software-Technologie entwickelt sich dynamisch \u2013 ich helfe Ihnen, die neuen M\u00f6glichkeiten gezielt f\u00fcr Ihren Erfolg einzusetzen.<br><\/p>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"6ec3347"}],"content_width":"full"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"2a4e2d92","settings":{"content_width":"full","title":"\u00dcber mich","header_size":"h4","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Roboto","typography_font_weight":"400","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"d5e6f7a"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"},{"id":"1321455b","settings":{"content_width":"full","editor":"<p>Ich bin Jan Foshag, selbst\u00e4ndiger Software-Entwickler. Ich lebe und arbeite in M\u00fcnchen.\u00a0Seit \u00fcber 20 Jahren entwickle ich Software \u2013 von klassischen Java-Anwendungen \u00fcber native iOS-Apps bis hin zu modernen KI-gest\u00fctzten L\u00f6sungen.<\/p>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"b9c0d1e"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"2e9df1e3","settings":{"content_width":"full","text":"Jetzt Kontakt aufnehmen","link":{"url":"#kontakt","is_external":"","nofollow":"","custom_attributes":""},"size":"md","align":"left","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Josefin Sans","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":16,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_letter_spacing":{"unit":"em","size":0.03,"sizes":[]},"background_color":"#0137d2","button_text_color":"#ffffff","border_radius":{"unit":"px","top":"100","right":"100","bottom":"100","left":"100","isLinked":true},"text_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"16","right":"30","bottom":"16","left":"30","isLinked":false},"display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"cta001cn"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"button","elType":"widget"},{"id":"7b6f2b07","settings":{"content_width":"full","title":"Apps","header_size":"h4","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Roboto","typography_font_weight":"400","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"de4b2ad"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"},{"id":"690a68d9","settings":{"content_width":"full","editor":"<p>Mit React Native oder Flutter entwickle ich Apps, die auf iOS und Android laufen \u2013 und dabei Prozesse vereinfachen und die Kundenn\u00e4he st\u00e4rken.<\/p>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"12a96ab"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"599758a9","settings":{"content_width":"full","title":"K\u00fcnstliche Intelligenz","header_size":"h4","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Roboto","typography_font_weight":"400","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"de4b2ad"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"},{"id":"fafcf7f","settings":{"content_width":"full","editor":"<p>Die Fortschritte der KI in den letzten Jahren sind beeindruckend \u2013 und das Tempo nimmt zu. KI-Agenten, die eigenst\u00e4ndig handeln und als Team<span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">\u00a0zusammenarbeiten, machen Dienstleistungen m\u00f6glich, die noch vor Kurzem undenkbar waren. Ich setze diese Technologien gezielt ein.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>KI erschlie\u00dft neue M\u00f6glichkeiten f\u00fcr bestehende Software. Ich unterst\u00fctze Sie beim Update und Ausbau vorhandener Anwendungen \u2014 von intelligenten Schnittstellen \u00fcber automatisierte Workflows\u00a0und KI-Assistenten bis hin zu interaktiven Dashboards, die Daten verst\u00e4ndlich aufbereiten.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 14px;\"><a style=\"display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #2563eb 100%); color: #ffffff; -webkit-text-fill-color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border: none; border-radius: 50px; padding: 4px 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.04em; box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.40);\" href=\"https:\/\/dashboards.fruchthandel-apps.de\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">KI-Dashboard ansehen \u2192<\/a><\/p>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"f95df64"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"34f010e9","settings":{"content_width":"full","title":"Projektbeispiele","header_size":"h4","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Roboto","typography_font_weight":"400","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"0a8d004"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"heading","elType":"widget"},{"id":"5195f022","settings":{"items":[{"item_title":"Fruchtgro\u00dfhandel","_id":"028b382"},{"item_title":"Stromanbieter","_id":"b82e58a"},{"item_title":"Patientenumfrage","_id":"5f21971"},{"_id":"4f06985","item_title":"Webanwendungen"},{"_id":"6139560","item_title":"GFK-Spiel"}],"display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"f777af7"}],"content_width":"full"},"elements":[{"id":"310aca44","settings":{"_title":"item #1","content_width":"full","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"9c817d2"}]},"elements":[{"id":"342ab0a7","settings":{"editor":"<ul>\n<li>Bestell-App f\u00fcr Fruchtgro\u00dfh\u00e4ndler (Fruchthof Ehinger)<\/li>\n<li>Entwickelt mit React Native<\/li>\n<li>Wachsende Bestellungen \u00fcber die App<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p><em>\"Ein sehr gutes, kompetentes Team, das unsere W\u00fcnsche und Anregungen nahezu perfekt umgesetzt hat. Auch bei den Kunden kommt unsere App sehr gut an, da sie ohne Komplikationen l\u00e4uft und es den Kunden sogar Spa\u00df macht mit der App zu arbeiten.\"<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"01b1077"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"container","isLocked":true},{"id":"73f955a2","settings":{"_title":"item #2","content_width":"full","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"a960702"}]},"elements":[{"id":"7a405d4e","settings":{"editor":"<ul>\n<li>Mitentwicklung einer Stromanbieter-App f\u00fcr eine gro\u00dfe Agentur (Plan.Net)<\/li>\n<li>Entwickelt mit React Native<\/li>\n<li>Server-Anbindung<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p><em>\"Wir halten den Entwickler im Bereich App-Entwicklung mit React Native f\u00fcr sehr qualifiziert und k\u00f6nnen ihn ohne Einschr\u00e4nkung weiterempfehlen.\"<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"438f502"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"container","isLocked":true},{"id":"2d7db126","settings":{"_title":"item #3","content_width":"full","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"d7a51de"}]},"elements":[{"id":"1b9dbd5b","settings":{"editor":"<ul>\n<li>Patientenumfrage-App f\u00fcr eine klinische Versorgungsstudie<\/li>\n<li>Entwickelt mit Flutter<\/li>\n<\/ul>","display_condition_list":[{"display_condition_login_status":"subscriber","_id":"e4a375f"}]},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","el